trans-unit.source: Used in order to associate or attach additional information to the instance of an object.
trans-unit.target: Brukes for å knytte eller knytte tilleggsinformasjon til forekomsten av et objekt.

trans-unit.source: This is used by the [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)] in order to keep track of interesting pieces of data during an editing session for data that is otherwise transient, that will (mostly) be discarded at the end of an editing session.
trans-unit.target: Dette brukes av den [!INCLUDE[wfd1](~/add/includes/wfd1-md.md)] for å holde oversikt over interessante typer data under en for dataene som ellers er midlertidig, som forkastes (vanligvis) på slutten av en redigering økt.

trans-unit.source: AttachedProperty is useful as items in the `View` can bind to the values and react to changes.
trans-unit.target: AttachedProperty er nyttig som elementer i den `View` kan bindes til verdiene og reagere endringer.

trans-unit.source: For instance, this is the way that the selected item template is displayed (it keys off of an attached property for selection).
trans-unit.target: Dette er for eksempel hvordan den valgte elementet malen vises (den nøkler fra en tilknyttet egenskap for valg).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the value of the specified model item.
trans-unit.target: Henter verdien for den angitte modellelementet.

trans-unit.source: The model item.
trans-unit.target: Modellelementet.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Object> that contains the value of the model item.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.Object>som inneholder verdien for modellelementet.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"></xref> is browsable.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en boolsk verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"> </xref> søkes gjennom.

trans-unit.source: The primary impact of setting this to `true` is that the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty> will be discoverable within the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Properties%2A> collection of the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> to which it is attached.
trans-unit.target: Primær virkningene av når du angir dette `true` er at den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty>vil være synlig i den <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Properties%2A>samling av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem>som den er knyttet.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.ModelItem.Properties%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"></xref> is browsable; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Model.AttachedProperty"> </xref> er søkes gjennom; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that determines whether the attached property is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som bestemmer om den tilknyttede egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the property is read-only; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis egenskapen er skrivebeskyttet. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the property.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.String> that contains the name of the property.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.String>som inneholder navnet på egenskapen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Creates a notification that indicates that the specified model item has changed.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en melding som angir at det angitte modellelementet er endret.

trans-unit.source: The item that has changed.
trans-unit.target: Elementet er endret.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the owner type.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir eiertypen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Type> that contains the owner type.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.Type>som inneholder eiertypen.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Resets the specified model item to the default value.
trans-unit.target: Tilbakestiller angitte modellelementet til standardverdien.

trans-unit.source: The model item to reset.
trans-unit.target: Modellelementet tilbakestille.

trans-unit.source: Sets the specified model item to the specified value.
trans-unit.target: Angir angitte modellelementet til den angitte verdien.

trans-unit.source: The model item to set.
trans-unit.target: Modellelementet angi.

trans-unit.source: The value to set.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal angis.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type.
trans-unit.target: Henter typen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Type> that contains the type.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.Type>som inneholder typen.</xref:System.Type>
